cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SI, cs.DS

The paper proposes a methodology for producing accurate probabilistic forecasts using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of recurrent neural networks, which suggests the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper deals with time series data, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
